        Sets the requests and body
        Parameters:
        userID - String containing the user ID of NS
        connectionID - String containing the selected Connection
        offerID - String containing the selected Offer
        seatreservation - String containing true or false, default is true.
        originCode - String containing the station code of the origin
        destinationCode - String containing the station code of the destination
